  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      QuickOptTM optimization method provides a quicker, simpler and reliable alternative to
      standard echocardiography methods for optimization of sensed AV, paced AV and V-V delays in
      patients with CRT-P devices
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
